            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> in half and season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until lightly browned</p>\n<p>Once browned, set aside on a plate</p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
